headline: The three finalists for Yahoo Finance's 2025 Company of the Year
summary: Yahoo Finance is putting a mirror up to 2025 and looking back on the biggest market stories, drivers, and outperformers. But only one can be named Yahoo Finance's Company of the Year. Yahoo Finance executive editor Brian Sozzi reveals the three finalists for Yahoo Finance's Company of the Year honor: private artificial intelligence developer OpenAI (OPAI.PVT), semiconductor juggernaut Nvidia (NVDA), and enterprise cloud titan Oracle (ORCL). The Company of the Year will be revealed on Monday, December 8. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Opening Bid.
